data.title: Attributed to? Marie, Princess, of Denmark, wife of Valdemar, Prince of Denmark, 1st daughter of Robert, Duke of Chartres (1865
data.meta_description: Photograph of Victoria Mary, Duchess of York (1867-1953) (right), Alexandra, Princess of Wales (1844-1925) (left) with Prince Edward of York (1894-1972) (right) and Princess Margrithe (1895-1992) in large hat; taken in Bernstorff Palace Gardens, near Copenhagen, Denmark.This was taken during a family gathering at Bernstorff to celebrate Queen Louise of Denmarks 81st birthday. Both Princess Alexandra and Princess Marie dOrleans, sister-in-law to Alexandra, took photographs of the events.
